<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pathien angsung thiengtho achun,
 Thihna chate chawl tanau;
 Maksa mahmah unau zie chun,
 Gawtmun meia a pawtnau.

[V2]
 Pathien pahchak,
 Van a chun hai ta puo'n a. (2)

[V3]
 2. Gitloh apat a tat ziekin,
 Hukdampa Lalpa Isu'n;
 Kumsawt mun a tuntieng uleh,
 Lasan chawian zing un au.

[V4]
 Kingkang tumhaw,
 Van achun haita puo'n a. (2)

[V5]
 3. Mihing lunggila lut ngeilo,
 Mita muhloh zak ngei loh;
 Lalpan Amah hehpihte ding,
 A na guot kha chang un au.

[V6]
 Nunkhuo nawpna,
 Kumsawt in pung zel ina. (2)

[V7]
 4. Pathien ma ah puonvam silhin,
 Sun zan zawmin um un au
 Gilkiel, dangchak thuok ta loin,
 Nawpna cheng nei zing ta'n au.

[V8]
 Gimtheih him him,
 Kumsawt in thuok ta puo'n au. (2)
 5. Jerusalem thak nuom achun,
 Thihna, lusun, thavaihna;
 Lunggim leh chawl heta loin,
 Chimchak puonau etnawp et.
 Lalpa hehpih,
 Hai loin chawian un au. (2)</lyrics>
<title>THE HOLY BOSOM OF GOD</title>
<author>Presby. Hymn Book 414 K.H. 388</author>
<hymn_number>388</hymn_number>
</song>